etadata: exact published date, volume\/issue,\n> `csaf039`, ISSNs, PDF filename\/path, version wording.\n> 13. Add the three new review pages as drafts:\n> \n> ```text\n> src\/content\/reviews\/godless-crusade.md\n> src\/content\/reviews\/hell-christian-ecology.md\n> src\/content\/reviews\/challenging-modernity.md\n> ```\n> \n> 14. Define consistent copyright, version, and review-page display rules before\n> publishing additional local review texts.\n> 15. Create `docs\/legacy-urls.md`; inventory old HTML pages, PDFs, CV paths,\n> image paths, and externally linked assets.\n> 16. Add static redirect stubs for GitHub Pages where needed; keep old PDF URLs\n> serving PDFs where feasible.\n> 17. Decide thesis-page scope for Stage 3.\n> \n> Option A: thesis remains bibliography-only during Stage 3.\n> \n> If so:\n> \n> - document that decision;\n> - do not include a thesis page in sitemap;\n> - do not link CV schema to a non-existent thesis page.\n> \n> Option B: thesis page is implemented during Stage 3.\n> \n> If so:\n> \n> - add the route;\n> - add or link the PDF if appropriate;\n> - add thesis metadata;\n> - include the ARK identifier;\n> - update `\/publications\/`;\n> - update CV schema;\n> - validate rendered JSON-LD.\n> \n> 18. Thesis page planned route if implemented:\n> \n> ```text\n> src\/pages\/thesis\/religious-atavism-climate-crisis\/index.astro\n> ```\n> \n> 19. Create\/update deployment documentation and launch checklist.\n> 20. Confirm GitHub Pages workflow, custom domain, DNS, and `public\/CNAME` needs.\n> 21. Fix or consciously defer small accessibility\/design issues, including Safari\n> homepage `h1.Name` visibility.\n> 22. Seminars consolidation remains undecided.\n> \n> ## 11. Immediate next steps\n> \n> Preferred Stage 3 sequence:\n> \n> 1. Run baseline checks:\n> \n> ```bash\n> npx astro sync\n> npx astro check\n> npm run build\n> ```\n> \n> 2. Run local inspection:\n> \n> ```bash\n> npm run dev\n> npm run preview\n> ```\n> \n> Inspect at least: